We view the Chinese market as important to our global growth strategy and are employing a multi-brand strategy. In the coming
years, we plan to leverage our global architectures to increase the number of product offerings under the Buick, Chevrolet and
Cadillac brands in China and continue to grow our business under the local Baojun and Wuling brands while we are accelerating the
development and rollout of EVs across our brands in China in response to our commitment to an all-electric future. We operate in
the Chinese market through a number of joint ventures and maintaining strong relationships with our joint venture partners is an
important part of our China growth strategy.
